   "body" : "Rather than maintaining 2 different versions of the same code (`.tiff` copying and symlink generation), consolidate to just the Python code, and use it on macOS and Linux. Previously Linux would  perform the 2 actions in the makefile, and then would still be running the `macdeployqtplus` script, so it makes sense to further consolidate deployment operations into the script.\r\n\r\nGuix Build on x86_64:\r\n```bash\r\nbash-5.1# find guix-build-$(git rev-parse --short=12 HEAD)/output/ -type f -print0 | env LC_ALL=C sort -z | xargs -r0 sha256sum\r\nc068a1d992784555c7e41711f31b600156e8eabde1f8792b6ea9942f53461684  guix-build-471491f47153/output/arm64-apple-darwin/SHA256SUMS.part\r\nf7ce98c40d45688cc62a35ff28243ae422c8f73505b27d8b4d90155b0f1d7536  guix-build-471491f47153/output/arm64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-arm64-apple-darwin-unsigned.dmg\r\n794a12391597cae0dde934289793bddc1a730ad149591196ebd14939a3f730ce  guix-build-471491f47153/output/arm64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-arm64-apple-darwin-unsigned.tar.gz\r\n8ce026bc38b58c512cbc7ccc75189ae053b21d0cd5a5a66e551028d414fdea32  guix-build-471491f47153/output/arm64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-arm64-apple-darwin.tar.gz\r\n43ef321e3275b9265fcb048cb1161fda005e8029b31b54dd4748a3b85a9c41db  guix-build-471491f47153/output/dist-archive/bitcoin-471491f47153.tar.gz\r\n2edb954a9a42b3933d4ef66d58102aec81380d8e35bb4ec1f8e82945fc4e39f8  guix-build-471491f47153/output/x86_64-apple-darwin/SHA256SUMS.part\r\na3d0df63e1bd8949b44ba19b1e7ef3b8bd5b0f6d924885ae6167b115a3dec6e6  guix-build-471491f47153/output/x86_64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-x86_64-apple-darwin-unsigned.dmg\r\n6628f08996863ed29afeaf48b76834c36fa3f49fffcc0089e040145a819cd06f  guix-build-471491f47153/output/x86_64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-x86_64-apple-darwin-unsigned.tar.gz\r\n76ff238a7698b6a98707b402b0c45aba5bb22fc79a151c1fef4d295245b95cf3  guix-build-471491f47153/output/x86_64-apple-darwin/bitcoin-471491f47153-x86_64-apple-darwin.tar.gz\r\n```",
